deploy wokflow

//using firebase

1. export app with command 
   pnpm run export 
   // this will write to ./out 

2. test files with 
   pnpm run test-bundle

3. deploy
   firebase deploy --only hosting    
   // usually you must specify one target, this is not the case. 


// when not using firebase
1 . create the bundle 
   npm run build 
2. test bundle
   npm start
